description:
When Jesus was born, only a few wise men in the East were watching the signs and wondered if this could be the promised one. Traveling from afar, they set out on a discovery mission to find out more. The wise men found baby Jesus and brought him gifts, gold, frankincense and myrrh. Their diligence and humility in seeking out the baby King leaves many lessons for us today.
